---
title: Double Asian-Style Glazed Chicken & Sesame Fries with Kohlrabi Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: Tonight’s dinner takes chicken and veg to new levels. As if chicken glazed in honey and soy sauce wasn’t delicious enough, serving it alongside sesame fries and a Japanese slaw adds another flavour punch! A dollop of garlic aioli adds the perfect amount of creaminess to this irresistible dish.
